# - Try to find the ubigraphclient library; Once done this will define
#
#  UBIGRAPHCLIENT_FOUND - system has the ubigraphclient library
#  UBIGRAPHCLIENT_INCLUDE_DIRS - the ubigraphclient include directory
#  UBIGRAPHCLIENT_LIBRARIES - The libraries needed to use ubigraphclient

